Package com.bonitasoft.engine.api

Class TenantAPIAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bonitasoft.engine.api.TenantAPIAccessor
  • public final class TenantAPIAccessor
extends Object
    Accessor class that retrieve APIs in Bonita Subscription Edition.
    Be aware that if you use TenantAPIAccessor instead, you will have only access to Community Edition APIs, which give access to less features.
    • ProcessAPI,
    • CommandAPI,
    • IdentityAPI,
    • MonitoringAPI,
    • LoginAPI,
    • ProfileAPI,
    • LogAPI,
    • ThemeAPI
    Author:
    Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
